## This is npm workspace monorepo
Dont use pnpm, dont cd to install packages

## Dev mode
`npm run dev`

## Unit tests
`npm run test`



## No comments
Don't write comments in code.
If you see comments that explain code  - remove them.
Only leave commented out code

## Functional tests
`npm run test:e2e`

### Single functional test
`npm run test:e2e -- path/to/feature.feature 

### Stop fiddling with timeouts
If something fail in test because of timeout - it means there is no such a thing.
Don't just increase timeout from 5 sec to 10, this is stupid, it is a local app where everything takes milliseconds.

### Dont run e2e tests with head or tail
You are not helping just make problems invisible - if you want to make it faster - run one feature or use --fail-fast to stop on first failure